Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.04,0:00:05.23,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,- 嗨 - 嘿\N{\fs21}- Hi. - Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.85,0:00:07.76,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,噢 好吃的\N{\fs21}Oh, yum.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.76,0:00:09.33,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,- 给我来点 - 不 Grace 别\N{\fs21}- Give me some. - No, Grace, don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.14,0:00:14.28,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,噢 天啊 太恶心了\N{\fs21}Oh God. That's disgusting.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.28,0:00:16.81,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,- 这是什么? - 水果奶昔\N{\fs21}- What is that? - Fruit shake.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.26,0:00:18.74,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,什么水果会是灰色的?\N{\fs21}What fruit is gray?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.72,0:00:21.81,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,梨\N{\fs21}Pears.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.86,0:00:24.84,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,什么?\N{\fs21}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.58,0:00:27.62,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,- 噢 - 噢 这是…\N{\fs21}- Oh. - Oh, for--
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.62,0:00:31.58,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,噢 蛋白粉?\N{\fs21}Oh, Mondo Fuel?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.60,0:00:34.14,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,你想变得壮起来\N{\fs21}You're trying to bulk up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.14,0:00:37.45,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,不 这只是膳食补充剂\N{\fs21}No, it's a dietary supplement.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.62,0:00:40.06,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,不 才不是\N{\fs21}No, it's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.03,0:00:43.21,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,你想要粗壮的臂膀\N{\fs21}You want za big arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.21,0:00:44.80,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,好让你勾搭阳刚的男人\N{\fs21}So you can get za big men,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.80,0:00:47.25,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,然后引诱他们到你的小窝里干柴烈火\N{\fs21}and lure them into your den of zoom-zoom.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.25,0:00:49.01,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,好的 非常感谢你的解说\N{\fs21}Okay, thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.01,0:00:50.57,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,够了 Grace\N{\fs21}That'll be enough, Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.57,0:00:52.50,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,- 噢 天啊 发生了什么? - 什么?\N{\fs21}- Oh my God, what's happening? - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.50,0:00:54.66,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,你的扣子都崩开了 衬衫也撕裂了\N{\fs21}Your buttons are popping. Your shirt is ripping.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.66,0:00:56.75,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,你要变成无敌浩克了! 你都变绿了!\N{\fs21}You're hulking up! You're turning green!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.01,0:01:01.65,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,谢谢你啊 顺带一提 这玩意儿碰巧也对你有好处的\N{\fs21}Thank you. Excuse me, this happens to be good for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.24,0:01:03.52,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,噢 天啊\N{\fs21}Oh my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.52,0:01:06.02,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,这上面说还能丰胸\N{\fs21}It says it also grows breast tissue.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.36,0:01:08.59,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,你想试试吗?\N{\fs21}You want to give it a try?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.71,0:01:17.51,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,你知道 我以为我了解你的一切\N{\fs21}You know I thought I knew everything about you,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.71,0:01:17.51,Note,,0,0,0,,引用英国首相丘吉尔名言 "It is a riddle, wrapped in a mystery, inside an enigma."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.51,0:01:20.36,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,但你其实是镜中花 水中月\N{\fs21}but you're a mystery, wrapped in a riddle,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.36,0:01:23.05,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,全身围绕着英格玛密码 还不断地在长胸\N{\fs21}surrounded by enigma, growing boobies.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.36,0:01:23.05,Note,,0,0,0,,二战中德国使用的加密编码机
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.42,0:01:26.46,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,话说回来 你怎么样?\N{\fs21}Anyway, how are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.46,0:01:29.37,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,还不错 Karen 要去度假了\N{\fs21}I'm okay. Karen's going on vacation,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.37,0:01:31.48,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,所以这周我要找个助理\N{\fs21}so I need to find an assistant for the week.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.48,0:01:34.10,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,Karen 整天做的就是锉指甲 翻购物册\N{\fs21}Karen files her nails, and thumbs through catalogues all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.10,0:01:35.42,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,她度假时都做什么?\N{\fs21}What's she gonna do on a vacation?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.92,0:01:37.57,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,我猜她会办公吧\N{\fs21}I guess office work.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.05,0:01:47.23,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,噢 天哪\N{\fs21}Oh my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.23,0:01:49.16,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,听着 免开尊口 站着说话不腰疼\N{\fs21}Look, don't. It's too easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.70,0:01:51.73,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,随便给我一件衣服穿\N{\fs21}Just give me something' to wear,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.73,0:01:52.93,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,因为我不想穿着这身\N{\fs21}'cause I can't walk another block
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.93,0:01:54.53,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,克林贡戏服再走一步路了\N{\fs21}in this Klingon suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.93,0:01:54.53,Note,,0,0,0,,《星际迷航》(Star Trek) 中的外星种族 生性好战
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.88,0:01:57.15,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,你打扮成这样 还指望我们不嘲笑你\N{\fs21}You want us to not make fun of you looking like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.15,0:01:59.95,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,那真是... 不合逻辑\N{\fs21}That would be... illogical.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.15,0:01:59.95,Note,,0,0,0,,《星际迷航》中 Spock 的常用词
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.95,0:02:04.01,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,坐下来 外星服务员 跟我们倒倒苦水\N{\fs21}Sit, alien cater-waiter. Tell us of your pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.67,0:02:07.57,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,都怪 Brandon Schwartz 的星舰主题成人礼\N{\fs21}Brandon Schwartz's Star Fleet bar mitzvah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.76,0:02:11.66,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,现场布置: 企业号航空母舰\N{\fs21}The decor, USS Enterprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.76,0:02:11.66,Note,,0,0,0,,《星际迷航》中舰艇名
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.66,0:02:13.94,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,菜单: 跨星系犹太洁食\N{\fs21}The menu, intergalactic kosher.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.73,0:02:15.28,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,更别提\N{\fs21}Not to mention,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.28,0:02:18.15,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,有个小博格人吐了我一身\N{\fs21}one of the little Borgs barfed all over my clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.28,0:02:18.15,Note,,0,0,0,,《星际迷航》中的高科技种族 半人半机械
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.69,0:02:20.85,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,舰长 经过近距离勘察\N{\fs21}Captain, after closer examination,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.85,0:02:23.17,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,我相信 我已经鉴定出了新物种\N{\fs21}I believe I have identified the life form as
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.81,0:02:24.65,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,"弯星人"\N{\fs21}"Gaylien."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.34,0:02:32.90,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,我们爱好和平 请不要重新布置我们的家具\N{\fs21}We come in peace. Please do not rearrange our furniture.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.33,0:02:37.22,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,好玩吧? 拜拜了\N{\fs21}You know what? Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.82,0:02:39.26,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,好 好 我们不玩了\N{\fs21}Okay, okay. We'll stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.26,0:02:40.94,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,不 你才不会呢 因为你就是无法自制\N{\fs21}No, you won't, because you can't help yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.94,0:02:42.29,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,你天生毒舌 卑鄙无耻\N{\fs21}You were born bitter, nasty,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.29,0:02:44.68,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,居心险恶 当然了 还有膀大腰圆\N{\fs21}mean- spirited and, of course, chunky.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.42,0:02:46.72,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,另外 Grace 你也没好到哪里去\N{\fs21}And, Grace, you're not much better.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.72,0:02:48.74,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,你就是个没有半分体面的小跟班\N{\fs21}You are a follower without an ounce of decency.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.74,0:02:50.89,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,Jack 你想到我办公室上一星期班吗?\N{\fs21}Jack, do you want to work in my office for a week?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.40,0:02:52.51,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,不过你倒是有改变自己的能力\N{\fs21}Although you have the ability to change,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.51,0:02:54.03,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,这就是我一直很喜欢你的地方\N{\fs21}and that's what I've always liked about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.46,0:02:55.36,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,Karen 去度假了\N{\fs21}Karen's going on vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.36,0:02:57.06,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,我需要有人帮我接接电话\N{\fs21}I need someone to help with the phones.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.06,0:02:57.92,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,-工作时间? - 很短\N{\fs21}- Hours? - Minimal.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.92,0:02:58.77,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,- 有牙医津贴? - 包午饭\N{\fs21}- Dental? - Lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.77,0:03:00.69,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,-我觉得我们可以谈拢 - 很好\N{\fs21}- I think we can work something out. - Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.93,0:03:03.04,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,噢 你们姐妹俩肯定玩得不亦乐乎\N{\fs21}Oh, you girls are gonna have a ball,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.04,0:03:05.11,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,相互编辫子 谈谈男孩子\N{\fs21}braidin' each other's hair, and talkin' about boys,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.11,0:03:06.94,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,做一做《时尚 COSMO》上的小测验\N{\fs21}and doin' the Cosmo quiz.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.94,0:03:09.03,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,比方说 "如何鉴定你的好朋友是不是贱人?"\N{\fs21}You mean like, "How To Tell lf Your Best Friend's A Bitch?"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.03,0:03:10.57,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,鉴定完毕 你是\N{\fs21}Yeah, already took it. You are.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.14,0:03:27.87,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,Karen Walker 想要见你\N{\fs21}Karen Walker's here to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.56,0:03:29.84,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,开玩笑吧\N{\fs21}You're kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.70,0:03:32.81,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,让她进来\N{\fs21}Send her in.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.50,0:03:35.30,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,他当然是啦\N{\fs21}Of course he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.30,0:03:37.88,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,比彩虹还要弯 亲爱的\N{\fs21}As a $3 bill, honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.30,0:03:37.88,Note,,0,0,0,,出自短语 "Queer as a three dollar bill" 就像三美元假币一样假\NQueer 双关假币/同志
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.60,0:03:43.74,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,她是刚从船上摔下来还是怎么了?\N{\fs21}Did she just fall off the boat or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.60,0:03:43.74,Note,,0,0,0,,Off the boat 暗指不了解风俗的移民 调侃看不出 Will 是同志
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.74,0:03:48.45,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,除了在办公室前台帮我出柜之外 有何贵干?\N{\fs21}What are you doing here besides outing me to the front office?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.80,0:03:51.81,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,好吧 首先… 噢 Will\N{\fs21}Well, first of-- oh, Will.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.13,0:03:52.80,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,绿色调\N{\fs21}The green,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.22,0:03:53.80,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,不行\N{\fs21}no.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.90,0:03:57.02,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,这些法律书籍倒还蛮可爱的\N{\fs21}The lawbooks are kind of cute, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.43,0:03:59.61,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,然后你竟然在地下室工作?\N{\fs21}And you work in a basement?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.61,0:04:01.69,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,亲爱的 你得搬到楼上去\N{\fs21}Honey, you've gotta move up from the street.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.69,0:04:03.30,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,要不然 你就得整天坐在这儿\N{\fs21}Otherwise, you're sittin' around all day
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.30,0:04:05.42,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,让廉价鞋子践踏你的眼睛\N{\fs21}watchin' bad shoes go by.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.74,0:04:08.49,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,看吧 玖熙\N{\fs21}See, Nine West.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.51,0:04:12.94,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,我喜欢这个办公室\N{\fs21}I love this office.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.94,0:04:16.16,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,看看这些雕花 这个地方历史厚重\N{\fs21}Look at these moldings. This place has historical significance.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.16,0:04:17.83,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,他们拍摄《冲突》的地方就在…\N{\fs21}They filmed "Serpico" Just a--
