Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.21,0:04:19.53,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,为什么我要替一栋楼辩护?\N{\fs21}why am I defending my building?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.53,0:04:21.45,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,Karen 你想要什么?\N{\fs21}Karen, what do you want?
