Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.20,0:04:26.70,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,噢 亲爱的\N{\fs21}Oh, honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.70,0:04:29.10,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,这儿太杂乱了 品味太差\N{\fs21}It's too busy, it's shoddy,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.10,0:04:30.79,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,我正在考虑离婚\N{\fs21}I'm thinking of leaving my husband,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.79,0:04:34.28,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,- 还有这些窗户的布置! - 什么? 什么?\N{\fs21}- and those window treatments! - What? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.29,0:04:37.60,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,竹子? 这是家律师事务所 又不是迪斯尼提基神殿\N{\fs21}Bamboo? This is a law firm, not The Tiki-Tiki Room.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.29,0:04:37.60,Note,,0,0,0,,Enchanted Tiki Room 迪斯尼乐园游乐设施 树屋景观
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.60,0:04:39.11,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,- Karen! - 你怎么能…\N{\fs21}- Karen! - How can you--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.20,0:04:42.66,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,别管窗帘了 说说你丈夫\N{\fs21}Forget the blinds. Your husband?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.66,0:04:43.94,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,你和 Stan 怎么了?\N{\fs21}What's happening with you and Stan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.59,0:04:48.58,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,我们本来准备登机 开启黑珍珠扫货之旅\N{\fs21}We were about to get on our plane to go black pearl shopping
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.58,0:04:49.62,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,前往波拉波拉岛\N{\fs21}in Bora Bora,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.62,0:04:51.91,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,突然之间 我看着 Stan\N{\fs21}when all of a sudden, I looked at Stan,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.91,0:04:53.64,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,恍然大悟\N{\fs21}and it dawned on me,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.90,0:04:56.43,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,婚姻不应该如此劳碌的\N{\fs21}marriage shouldn't be this much work.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.97,0:04:59.96,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,Karen 我是个公司委托律师\N{\fs21}Karen, I'm a corporate attorney.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.96,0:05:01.71,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,你需要的是一位出色的离婚律师\N{\fs21}What you need is a good divorce lawyer
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.71,0:05:04.69,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,或者只是一位出色的药剂师\N{\fs21}or perhaps just a good pharmacist.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.36,0:05:10.34,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,你们这种人毒舌起来都不打结的\N{\fs21}The nastiness comes so easily to your people.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.90,0:05:16.15,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,拜托 Will 不要装得屈尊降贵\N{\fs21}Come on, Will. Don't patronize me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.15,0:05:18.70,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,我非常清楚你是哪种律师\N{\fs21}I know exactly what kind of lawyer you are,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.70,0:05:20.20,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,没名气的那种\N{\fs21}an obscure one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.90,0:05:22.48,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,所以我才需要你\N{\fs21}And that's why I need you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.48,0:05:24.87,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,我得弄清楚 Stan 的公司财产\N{\fs21}I have to find out about Stan's corporate holdings
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.87,0:05:27.09,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,- 还不能让他发现 - 真的吗?\N{\fs21}- without him knowing. - Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.09,0:05:30.10,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,真有王雪琴的风范\N{\fs21}This is so Alexis Carrington.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.19,0:05:30.00,Note,,0,0,0,,八十年代美剧《豪门恩怨》(Dallas) 中人物 石油大亨前妻
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.10,0:05:32.75,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,别闹 听着 我是认真的\N{\fs21}Come on. Look, I'm serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.75,0:05:37.25,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,我开始觉得 我好像已经不再拥有我的丈夫了\N{\fs21}I'm starting to feel as if I don't own my own husband anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.60,0:05:42.90,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,你是说 你已经不再了解你的丈夫了\N{\fs21}You mean you don't know your own husband anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.90,0:05:45.41,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,- 我刚才就是这么说的啊 亲爱的 - 不 你…\N{\fs21}- That's what I just said, honey. - No, you--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.91,0:05:48.45,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,你说的是"拥有"\N{\fs21}you said "Own."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.47,0:05:51.25,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,不 我说的是 我感觉我不再拥有我自己的… 好像我…\N{\fs21}No, I said I feel like I don't own my own-- Like I don't--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.33,0:05:52.93,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,哎呀 好了 叮铃铃\N{\fs21}Oh, all right! Ding! Ding! Ding!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.93,0:05:54.99,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,你会一站到底的 机灵鬼!\N{\fs21}You'd win on Jeopardy, smart guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.93,0:05:54.99,Note,,0,0,0,,《危险边缘》(Jeopardy) 益智问答游戏节目
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.73,0:06:01.44,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,当事人保密特权什么时候才生效?\N{\fs21}When does the attorney's client privilege kick in?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.91,0:06:05.29,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,收到支票 即时生效\N{\fs21}As soon as the client gives the attorney a check,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.63,0:06:06.99,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,但… 不 Karen\N{\fs21}but-- no, Karen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.99,0:06:08.92,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,让我当你的律师…\N{\fs21}Me as your lawyer--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.46,0:06:11.71,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,让我当你的律师 就这么定了\N{\fs21}me as your lawyer, consider it done.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.85,0:06:14.61,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,我告诉你一些你可能不知道的 Will 逸事\N{\fs21}Here's something you probably don't know about Will.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.61,0:06:17.80,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,上小学的时候 Will 暗地里超喜欢一本书…\N{\fs21}In elementary school, Will secretly loved the book--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.80,0:06:19.43,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,《上帝 您在吗? 是我 玛格丽特》\N{\fs21}"Are You There, God? It's Me, Margaret".
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.69,0:06:21.37,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,大学时这本书让我们心手相牵\N{\fs21}We bonded over it in college.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.16,0:06:24.39,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,- 那好 你知不知道Will… - 噢 拜托\N{\fs21}- Okay, did you know that Will-- - Oh, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.39,0:06:26.40,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,等到你比我更了解 Will 的那天\N{\fs21}The day you know more about Will than I do,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.40,0:06:28.28,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,我会很乐意亲你屁股\N{\fs21}is the day I gladly kiss your butt.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.88,0:06:31.88,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,帮帮忙 把流苏分好类\N{\fs21}Do me a favor. Sort these tassels.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.88,0:06:34.05,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,你想要按颜色分 还是按尺寸分?\N{\fs21}You want me to sort them by color or by size?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.05,0:06:35.32,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,按5点之前分好的标准分\N{\fs21}By 5:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.96,0:06:38.66,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,你想表现表现吗? 去帮帮你身后那个人\N{\fs21}You want to be useful? Help the man standing behind you
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.66,0:06:39.97,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,他的包裹很大\N{\fs21}with the big package.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.66,0:06:39.97,Note,,0,0,0,,Package 双关 包裹/鼓裆内的活儿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.42,0:06:41.87,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,Grace 别调戏我\N{\fs21}Grace, don't tease me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.75,0:06:49.86,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,- 你好 - 是 Grace Adler 设计室吗?\N{\fs21}- Hello. - Grace Adler Design?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.04,0:06:51.14,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,我来签收吧\N{\fs21}I'll sign for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.97,0:06:55.99,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,签名字就行了 先生 我不需要你的号码\N{\fs21}Just your name, sir. I don't need your phone number.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.55,0:06:59.80,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,别这么确定\N{\fs21}Don't be so sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.18,0:07:02.10,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,先生\N{\fs21}sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.42,0:07:05.25,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,Jack?\N{\fs21}Jack?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.87,0:07:08.13,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,Jack? Jack!\N{\fs21}Jack? Jack!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.13,0:07:10.40,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,嗨 你能帮我把它放在后面吗?\N{\fs21}Hi. Can you put that in the back, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.40,0:07:11.27,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,谢谢你\N{\fs21}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.01,0:07:17.96,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,哇噢 要我说 那家伙和 Steven 长得一模一样\N{\fs21}Wow, tell me that guy did not look exactly like Steven.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.96,0:07:19.80,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,- 哪个 Steven? - Will 的 Steven\N{\fs21}- Who's Steven? - Will's Steven.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.80,0:07:22.35,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,- Will 没有什么 Steven - 好吧 不再有了\N{\fs21}- Will doesn't have a Steven. - Well, not anymore,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.35,0:07:23.45,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,你懂的...\N{\fs21}but you know--
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.74,0:07:25.59,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,噢\N{\fs21}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.94,0:07:30.67,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,你不知道谁是 Steven\N{\fs21}You don't know who Steven is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.50,0:07:33.34,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,唔 手滑\N{\fs21}Oops, butterfingers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.53,0:07:37.33,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,我猜呀 空头支票还是不要乱开\N{\fs21}I guess one shouldn't make any promises they can't keep.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.53,0:07:45.66,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,心中有爱 面带微笑 来吧\N{\fs21}With love in your heart, and a smile on your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.55,0:07:48.79,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,快告诉我 Steven 是谁就行了\N{\fs21}Just tell me who Steven is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.24,0:07:50.09,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,我正翘臀以待呢\N{\fs21}I'm waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.66,0:07:53.73,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,- 每小时加两块 - 听我道来\N{\fs21}- Two bucks more an hour. - I'm talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.73,0:07:55.17,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,Steven 是他以前事务所的同事\N{\fs21}Steven was a guy at his old law firm.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.17,0:07:55.87,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,他们有过那么一小段\N{\fs21}They had a little fling
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.87,0:07:57.97,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,去年夏天的事 那时他还和 Michael 在一起\N{\fs21}last summer while he was still seeing Michael.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.19,0:08:00.81,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,让我用四个字形容 鲜嫩多汁\N{\fs21}And let me just say, Hotty McHot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.81,0:08:02.25,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,咝\N{\fs21}Ss-sss.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.60,0:08:06.23,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,- 去年夏天? - 是的\N{\fs21}- Last summer? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.23,0:08:08.46,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,他那时称他是"客户" 这是他的暗号\N{\fs21}He used to call him a client. That was his code word.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.46,0:08:09.66,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,"我要和一个客户吃晚饭"\N{\fs21}"I'm having dinner with a client.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.66,0:08:11.88,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,"我要给一个客户起草陈述"\N{\fs21}I'm drawing up some briefs for a client."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.06,0:08:14.03,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,的确是和"陈述"有关\N{\fs21}There were some briefs involved,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.06,0:08:14.03,Note,,0,0,0,,Brief 双关 案件陈述/短裤
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.89,0:08:17.42,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,只不过他并没做"起草"那部分\N{\fs21}but he wasn't drawin' them up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.35,0:08:25.63,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,- 嘿 - 嗨\N{\fs21}- Hey. - Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.33,0:08:28.70,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,准备好听听我计划的二人之夜了吗?\N{\fs21}Ready to hear what I have planned for us tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.25,0:08:31.58,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,首先 我要无视我所有的饮食问题\N{\fs21}First of all, I'm putting aside all of my food issues.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.58,0:08:34.07,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,准备好 今晚 我们吃小麦\N{\fs21}So get ready, tonight, we eat wheat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.58,0:08:34.07,Note,,0,0,0,,圣经中用 wheat 比喻纯朴诚实的信徒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.73,0:08:36.45,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,那么\N{\fs21}So
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.46,0:08:37.62,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,和 Jack 一起工作\N{\fs21}Workin' with Jack.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.01,0:08:38.59,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,他等了多长时间\N{\fs21}How long did it take
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.59,0:08:40.48,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,才忍不住扯了一匹你的丝绸帷幔\N{\fs21}before he took one of your silk drapery panels,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.48,0:08:42.20,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,围在身上当纱笼穿的?\N{\fs21}and wore it like a sarong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.48,0:08:42.20,Note,,0,0,0,,印尼及马来西亚地区民族服装
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.10,0:08:48.99,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,你干嘛用这种眼神看我?\N{\fs21}Why are you looking at me like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.99,0:08:51.28,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,《我知道你去年夏天干了什么》\N{\fs21}"I Know What You Did Last Summer."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.99,0:08:51.28,Note,,0,0,0,,1997年惊悚片
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.61,0:08:56.60,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,什么?\N{\fs21}Pardon?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.28,0:09:00.51,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,那部电影 我租的\N{\fs21}The movie. I rented it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.51,0:09:03.08,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,-《我知道你去年夏天干了什么》 - "去年夏天" 噢 我懂了\N{\fs21}- "I Know What You Did Last Summer." - "Last Summer," Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.98,0:09:06.60,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,和这部《风流韵事》\N{\fs21}And "An Affair To Remember."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.98,0:09:06.60,Note,,0,0,0,,1957年爱情片
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.24,0:09:11.89,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,以及这部《客户》\N{\fs21}With "The Client."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.24,0:09:11.89,Note,,0,0,0,,1994年警匪片
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.41,0:09:19.96,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,- 你觉得怎么样? - 我觉得好电影都被别人借了\N{\fs21}- What do you think? - All the good movies were taken.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.98,0:09:24.34,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,我还觉得今晚你得一个人看这些电影了\N{\fs21}I think you're also gonna have to watch them alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.34,0:09:27.74,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,- 为什么 你要去哪? - 我要去见一个客户\N{\fs21}- Why, where you going? - I gotta meet with a client.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.66,0:09:32.63,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,一个什么?\N{\fs21}A what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.33,0:09:35.14,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,一个客户\N{\fs21}A client.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.04,0:09:38.00,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,- 晚上九点? - 是啊\N{\fs21}-At 9:00 at night? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.02,0:09:39.35,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,只有这时候我们俩才都有空\N{\fs21}It's the only time we could both do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.31,0:09:44.10,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,- 是谁? - 就是个客户而已\N{\fs21}- Who is it? - It's just a client.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.10,0:09:46.54,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,一个新客户 明天早上再见\N{\fs21}It's a new client. I'll see you in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.87,0:09:49.39,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,噢 小麦别吃太多 行吗?\N{\fs21}Oh, and go easy on the wheat, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.39,0:09:50.91,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,我不想回到家 发现你躺在地上\N{\fs21}I don't want to come home, and find you lying on the floor
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.91,0:09:53.38,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,攥着手机 手指才摁到9\N{\fs21}clutching the phone with your finger on the nine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.91,0:09:53.38,Note,,0,0,0,,麸质过敏症 与 小麦过敏\N美国急救电话911
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.32,0:10:01.00,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,Jack 太好了 你还在\N{\fs21}Jack, good, you're still there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.50,0:10:02.22,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\fs21}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.30,0:10:06.54,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,我还在等那个大包裹\N{\fs21}I'm still waiting for that package.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.95,0:10:10.20,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,Grace 你这些丝绸帷幔在哪搞到的?\N{\fs21}Grace, where did you get these drapery panels?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.15,0:10:12.95,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,- 翡翠纺织 怎么了? - 没事\N{\fs21}- Emerald Fabric, why? - No reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.90,0:10:16.28,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,你问到 Steven 的时候 Will 什么反应?\N{\fs21}What did Will say when you asked him about Steven?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.28,0:10:18.99,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,我一直没机会问他那个客户的事 为什么?\N{\fs21}I never got to ask him about that client. Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.99,0:10:21.03,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,- 因为他有了个新客户 - 你说什么?\N{\fs21}- Because he has a new client. - What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.03,0:10:23.58,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,噢 别跟我装傻 他在约会 Jack\N{\fs21}Oh, like you don't know. He's seeing someone, Jack.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.58,0:10:24.76,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,我不敢相信你又瞒着我\N{\fs21}I can't believe you kept this from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.76,0:10:25.91,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,我什么都不知道\N{\fs21}I didn't know anything about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.91,0:10:27.28,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,不 肯定是别的什么\N{\fs21}No, it's gotta be something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.28,0:10:28.74,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,再说 他交桃花运的几率太小了\N{\fs21}Besides, the odds are against him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.74,0:10:30.91,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,过去八年 他只和五个人在一起过\N{\fs21}He's only been with five people in the last eight years.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.91,0:10:32.74,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,他就像一只没人爱的座头鲸\N{\fs21}He's like a humpback whale.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.93,0:10:36.13,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,没人"做"的座头鲸\N{\fs21}Without the hump.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.19,0:10:41.29,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,噢 天哪 那究竟是发生了什么?\N{\fs21}Oh my God. So what could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.52,0:10:44.78,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,会是什么事 他既不告诉你 也不告诉我?\N{\fs21}What could it be that he didn't tell you, and he didn't tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.97,0:10:48.50,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,肯定是他不想让我们知道的事\N{\fs21}It must be something he didn't want us to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.76,0:10:52.34,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,干得漂亮 少女妙探 我们待会在老神秘河上汇合\N{\fs21}Good work, Nancy Drew. Let's meet up at Old Mystery Creek.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.76,0:10:52.34,Note,,0,0,0,,悬疑小说人物 最早出现于1930年 后出版多部小说和相关影视剧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.52,0:10:57.64,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,Jack 赶紧过来\N{\fs21}Jack, just get over here now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.81,0:10:58.76,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,还有放下帷幔\N{\fs21}And lose the drapes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.76,0:11:00.88,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,我在电话里都听见它们摩擦的声音\N{\fs21}I can hear the fabrics rustling through the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.55,0:11:10.54,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,我能不能…\N{\fs21}Can I--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.92,0:11:13.15,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,我们能作为朋友聊一会吗?\N{\fs21}Can I talk to you for a minute as if we were friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.15,0:11:14.64,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,噢 亲爱的\N{\fs21}Oh, honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.89,0:11:16.66,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,我知道 我知道 我没有给你好脸色看\N{\fs21}I know, I know, I give you a hard time,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.66,0:11:19.41,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,我还嘲笑你从来不干任何工作\N{\fs21}and I make jokes about how you never do any work.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.41,0:11:21.61,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,很好笑 因为这是实话\N{\fs21}But it's funny because it's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.31,0:11:25.34,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\fs21}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.38,0:11:29.46,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,如果你决定要离婚 我可以帮你\N{\fs21}If you're set on divorce, I can help you with that,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.46,0:11:32.83,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,但是感情上需要承担很多\N{\fs21}but it's gonna take an emotional toll.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.83,0:11:34.48,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,噢 我不知道 Will\N{\fs21}Oh, I don't know, Will.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.48,0:11:37.46,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,从许多层面讲 我都过得很好\N{\fs21}In a lot of ways, I have a very good life.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.46,0:11:40.63,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,城里一套房 郊区一套房 轮船\N{\fs21}A home in the city, a home in the country, a boat,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.63,0:11:43.68,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,珠宝 艺术品 豪车 一个厨子 一个教练\N{\fs21}jewelry, art, cars, a chef, a trainer,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.68,0:11:45.51,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,- 一个碉堡的衣橱… - 是是 我知道\N{\fs21}- an ass-kicking wardrobe-- - Yeah, I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.66,0:11:51.66,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,那这个碉堡衣橱里的女人 是怎么样的呢?\N{\fs21}How is the woman inside the ass-kicking wardrobe?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.82,0:11:56.02,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,体脂率 9% 感觉有些迷茫\N{\fs21}9% body fat and a little bit lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.12,0:12:00.62,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,Will 我不知道建立亲密关系需要付出什么\N{\fs21}Will, I don't know what it takes to make a good relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.39,0:12:02.66,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,我也不是专家\N{\fs21}I'm no expert,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.34,0:12:05.32,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,但我生命中最重要的关系\N{\fs21}but the key relationships in my life
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.32,0:12:08.65,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,就是建立在交流和信任之上的\N{\fs21}are based on communication and trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.65,0:12:10.93,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,他藏了些什么? 什么事会如此糟糕?\N{\fs21}What is he hiding? What could be so bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.93,0:12:12.57,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,为什么他不信任我?\N{\fs21}Why doesn't he trust me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.40,0:12:17.75,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,不知道 可能是因为你正在翻他的东西吧\N{\fs21}I don't know. Maybe it's 'cause you're rifling through his stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.83,0:12:20.13,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,别误会 这事我经常干\N{\fs21}Don't get me wrong, I do this all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.13,0:12:21.81,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,只不过你们从来没逮着我\N{\fs21}You're just never here when it happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.03,0:12:25.37,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,噢 别担心 你的房间 无聊\N{\fs21}Oh, don't worry. Your room, boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.81,0:12:31.09,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,再跟我说一遍 我们在找什么\N{\fs21}So, tell me again what we're looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.09,0:12:32.69,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,宣告噩耗的东西\N{\fs21}Something that spells doom.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.44,0:12:35.01,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,什么?\N{\fs21}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.01,0:12:36.68,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,他把所有的巧克力软糖都吃光了\N{\fs21}He ate all the Mallomars.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.53,0:12:39.52,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,天哪 他在压力性暴食\N{\fs21}Oh my God. He's stress eating.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.52,0:12:42.54,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,他暴饮暴食是因为… 他的事业面临困境\N{\fs21}He's eating because-- his business is folding.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.54,0:12:44.44,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,- 你觉得他的事业面临困境了? - 全都解释得通了\N{\fs21}- You think his business is folding? - It all makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.44,0:12:47.45,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,他的确是问过我 什么时候才能还欠他的25,000美元\N{\fs21}He actually asked me when I would pay back the 25,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.20,0:12:52.58,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,不... 这种事他会告诉我的 肯定是更严重的事\N{\fs21}No... That, he would tell me. It has to be something worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.58,0:12:54.35,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,天啊 他到底瞒着我什么?\N{\fs21}God, what is he keeping from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.15,0:12:58.00,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,噢 天哪 是毒品\N{\fs21}Oh my God. It's drugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.62,0:13:02.11,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,是毒品 他在吸毒\N{\fs21}It's drugs. He's doing drugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.11,0:13:03.28,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,居然不带我\N{\fs21}Without me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.84,0:13:09.35,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,不是说我想吸 但至少也先问问我嘛\N{\fs21}Not that I do drugs, but I'd like to be asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.19,0:13:12.91,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,你知道还有什么事他不会告诉我们吗? 他生病了\N{\fs21}You know what else he wouldn't tell either of us? If he's sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.42,0:13:16.61,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,他需要换肾 噢 天哪 他需要换肾\N{\fs21}He needs a kidney. Oh my God, he needs a kidney.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.67,0:13:20.25,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,不是说我会捐 但至少也先问问我嘛\N{\fs21}Not that I would give him a kidney, but I'd like to be asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.86,0:13:23.98,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,- Jack 快去检查他的卧室 - 好吧 我要找什么?\N{\fs21}- Jack, go check his bedroom. - Okay what am I looking for?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.98,0:13:24.97,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,噩耗\N{\fs21}Doom.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.67,0:13:27.08,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,从他的床开始\N{\fs21}I'll start with his bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.14,0:13:30.56,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,啊哈! 找到了!\N{\fs21}A-ha! I found something!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.56,0:13:32.85,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,- 什么?! - Will 的新外套\N{\fs21}- What?! - Will's new jacket.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.12,0:13:35.22,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,我穿着有点大 但爱死这面料了\N{\fs21}I'm swimming in it, but loving the fabric.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.41,0:13:39.90,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,我觉得这里什么都没有\N{\fs21}I don't think there's anything here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.90,0:13:42.42,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,噢 难怪这儿鼓鼓囊囊的 他的日程本在口袋里\N{\fs21}Oh, no wonder it's so bulky. His day planner's in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.59,0:13:55.73,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,- 这是不对的 - 你觉得我们应该把它收起来?\N{\fs21}- This is wrong. - You think we should put it away?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.73,0:13:57.53,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,不 月份不对\N{\fs21}No, it's the wrong month.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.56,0:14:03.07,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,好的 在这里 他会在 Astor 咖啡厅吃晚饭\N{\fs21}Okay, here it is. He's having dinner at the Astor Cafe...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.12,0:14:07.90,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,- 和K一起 - K? 肾!\N{\fs21}- with K. - K? Kidney!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.01,0:14:09.70,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,但是他不可能和肾一起吃饭啊\N{\fs21}But he wouldn't be having dinner with one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.75,0:14:13.17,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,Astor 咖啡厅\N{\fs21}The Astor Cafe.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.94,0:14:15.23,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,- 不 我不行 - 你可以的\N{\fs21}- No, I can't. - You could.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.23,0:14:15.86,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,- 我不会这样做 - 你会的\N{\fs21}- I won't. - You will.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.86,0:14:16.94,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,- 你说得对 - 好\N{\fs21}- You're right. - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.39,0:14:20.35,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,看起来尽管如此\N{\fs21}It seems like despite everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.35,0:14:21.78,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,你还是爱着你丈夫的\N{\fs21}you're still in love with your husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.56,0:14:24.69,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,我觉得很多层面上 我都有点像一个年轻版\N{\fs21}I guess in a lot of ways I'm kind of like a younger,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.69,0:14:27.36,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,更加美艳版的 Leona Helmsley\N{\fs21}much more beautiful version of Leona Helmsley.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.69,0:14:27.36,Note,,0,0,0,,美国酒店业女富豪 以浮华生活和暴戾性格闻名 人称"苛刻女皇"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.59,0:14:30.02,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,首先 你为钱结婚\N{\fs21}First, you marry for money,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.02,0:14:33.20,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,然后 你发现自己爱上了这个糟老头\N{\fs21}and then you find yourself lovin' the old coot.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.62,0:14:36.23,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,接着 他就暴毙 最后 你分到了家产\N{\fs21}Then he drops dead, and you get the money anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.23,0:14:39.58,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,- 这是个双赢 - 我太感动了\N{\fs21}- It's a win-win. - My heart is full.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.58,0:14:42.79,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,手机给我 我现在就想给 Stan 打电话\N{\fs21}Give me your phone. I wanna call Stan right this minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.91,0:14:46.35,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,- 头 头 头 - 有什么事吗?\N{\fs21}- Head, head, head. - Can I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.35,0:14:49.13,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,- 不 我只是来这里找人的 - 你需要预约\N{\fs21}- No, I'm just here to see someone. - You need a reservation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.26,0:14:50.62,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,找人也要预约?\N{\fs21}To see someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.82,0:14:52.27,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,我们要保护我们的顾客\N{\fs21}We like to protect our patrons.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.27,0:14:53.15,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,你觉得我能干什么?\N{\fs21}What do you think I'm gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.15,0:14:55.45,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,在餐厅里跑来跑去 然后在他们的食物里撒盐?\N{\fs21}Run around the dining room, and oversalt their food?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.84,0:14:58.78,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,谁是我的狗狗 哈?\N{\fs21}Who's my puppy, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.85,0:15:02.99,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,谁是我淘气 下流的小狗狗?\N{\fs21}Who's my naughty, naughty little puppy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.25,0:15:09.83,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,尾巴摇起来\N{\fs21}Wag that tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.38,0:15:14.44,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,就这样 给我摇\N{\fs21}That's right, wag it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.25,0:15:18.27,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,啊噢\N{\fs21}Uh-oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.27,0:15:23.16,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,噢 我认识一只非常 非常顽皮 又淘气的狗狗\N{\fs21}Oh, I know a very, very bad, naughty puppy
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.16,0:15:25.97,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,又要戴上他的项圈了\N{\fs21}who's gonna have to go back on his leash.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.62,0:15:29.02,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,不好意思 我可以结账了吗?\N{\fs21}Excuse me, could I get the check?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.06,0:15:31.00,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,另外我需要一架离开这里的飞机\N{\fs21}And an airlift out of here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.05,0:15:34.76,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,噢 Stan?\N{\fs21}Oh, Stan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.76,0:15:37.00,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,待会再打给你 我又接到了一通电话\N{\fs21}I'm gonna have to call you back. I'm gettin' another call,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.00,0:15:39.56,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,回头见 嗯哼\N{\fs21}but I'll see you later. Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.56,0:15:41.37,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,开始做仰卧起坐吧\N{\fs21}Start doing your sit-ups.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.17,0:15:47.73,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,给你 亲爱的 有你的电话 我得去补个妆\N{\fs21}Here, honey, you got a call. And I have to go re-apply.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.20,0:15:48.86,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,你好\N{\fs21}Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.86,0:15:50.36,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,嗨 是我\N{\fs21}Hi, it's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.56,0:15:52.79,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,我只想知道 你有没有\N{\fs21}I just wanted to know if there was,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.79,0:15:55.25,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,就是 有没有什么事想告诉我\N{\fs21}you know, anything that you wanted to tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.90,0:15:58.06,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,- 你在说什么事? - 你有事瞒着我\N{\fs21}- What are you talking about? - You're hiding something from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.06,0:16:00.72,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,- 是什么事? - 你吃了多少小麦?\N{\fs21}- What is it? - How much wheat did you have?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.53,0:16:03.29,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,为什么不告诉我 Steven 的事?\N{\fs21}Why didn't you tell me about Steven?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.29,0:16:05.69,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,- Steven? - 对啊! 我还是从…\N{\fs21}- Steven? - Yes! I had to find out from--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.94,0:16:09.06,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,噢! 见鬼!\N{\fs21}oh! Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.56,0:16:10.13,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,我再也不会\N{\fs21}That's the last time
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.13,0:16:12.57,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,为了一双赠品连裤袜 而买一部手机了\N{\fs21}I buy a phone to get a free pair of pantyhose.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.98,0:16:23.58,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,喂?\N{\fs21}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.58,0:16:25.97,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,我们的约法三章里可没有相互隐瞒\N{\fs21}Keeping secrets is not in our rule book.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.17,0:16:27.83,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,关于 K 的事我都知道了\N{\fs21}I know all about K.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.26,0:16:30.38,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,好吧 其实 我并不是什么都知道\N{\fs21}Well, actually, I don't know all about K.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.38,0:16:32.31,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,事实上 关于 K 我什么都不知道 谁是 K?\N{\fs21}Actually, I don't know anything about K. Who's K?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.26,0:16:35.53,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,等一下 喂?\N{\fs21}Hold on. Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.53,0:16:39.22,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,什么? 不 我不是… 稍等\N{\fs21}What? No, I don't-- wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.46,0:16:45.54,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,所有位置都订满了\N{\fs21}We're all booked up,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.54,0:16:47.21,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,不过看起来十点钟有个空缺\N{\fs21}but it looks like we have an opening at 10:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.86,0:16:49.21,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,名字是 Bochner 两位\N{\fs21}Bochner for two.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.53,0:16:52.75,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,靠窗的座位? 别得寸进尺了\N{\fs21}Window seat? Don't push it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.58,0:16:57.93,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,- Will… - 我正在吃晚餐\N{\fs21}- Will-- - I am in the middle of dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.93,0:16:59.72,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,不 才不是 你已经在喝咖啡了\N{\fs21}No, you're not. You're already on coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.72,0:17:02.00,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,好吧 我已经在喝咖… 你在哪?\N{\fs21}Okay, so I'm on cof-- where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.81,0:17:04.88,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,这是秘密\N{\fs21}It's a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.36,0:17:09.11,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,现在 告诉我 这感觉可不好受吧?\N{\fs21}Now, tell me. How does that make you feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.28,0:17:11.57,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,我感觉像是劣质血腥片里的联谊会女孩\N{\fs21}Like a sorority girl in a bad slasher movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.57,0:17:12.76,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,你在哪里?!\N{\fs21}Where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.11,0:17:15.57,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,这么说吧\N{\fs21}Let's just put it this way,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.57,0:17:19.97,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,"这通电话就是从这间屋子里打来的"\N{\fs21}"the call is coming from inside the house."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.57,0:17:19.97,Note,,0,0,0,,1979年惊悚电影《来电惊魂》(When a Stranger Calls) 经典桥段
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.45,0:17:27.01,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,Grace 你现在不能呆在这\N{\fs21}Grace, you cannot be here right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.01,0:17:28.19,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,- 快回去 - 不\N{\fs21}- Go home. - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.33,0:17:29.06,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,- 回去! - 不\N{\fs21}- Go home! - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.06,0:17:30.08,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,- 走! - 不\N{\fs21}- Go! - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.09,0:17:31.83,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,不好意思\N{\fs21}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.83,0:17:34.40,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,请问你能把那个红发女疯子赶走吗?\N{\fs21}Would you mind having that crazed redhead removed?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.40,0:17:36.17,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,听我说 我是 Ricky Ricardo\N{\fs21}Listen to me, I'm Ricky Ricardo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.40,0:17:36.17,Note,,0,0,0,,美国经典情景喜剧 I Love Lucy 男主角
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.57,0:17:38.45,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,- 我会处理好的 Ricardo先生 - 不\N{\fs21}- I'll take care of it, Mr. Ricardo. - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.12,0:17:40.41,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,不好意思\N{\fs21}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.74,0:17:44.76,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,算了吧 这太不理智了 请让她进来吧\N{\fs21}Look, this is insane. Let her in, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.71,0:17:57.73,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,好的 发生了什么事? 你需要一个肺吗?\N{\fs21}Okay, what is it? Do you need a lung?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.73,0:18:00.21,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,我有两个 选一个 只要不再瞒东瞒西就好\N{\fs21}I have two. Pick one. Just no more secrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.21,0:18:02.47,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,- Grace 我什么都告诉你了 - K是谁?\N{\fs21}- Grace, I tell you everything. - Who is K?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.47,0:18:04.03,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,我不能告诉你\N{\fs21}I can't tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.03,0:18:06.58,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,Grace 你来这里做什么?\N{\fs21}Grace, what are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.58,0:18:09.46,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,亲爱的 你怎么了? 你看起来像张没铺的床\N{\fs21}Honey, what happened to you? You look like an unmade bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.90,0:18:13.30,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,Karen 你不是去度假了吗\N{\fs21}Karen, you're supposed to be on vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.30,0:18:15.87,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,Grace 向你介绍我的客户 K\N{\fs21}Grace, I'd like you to meet my client, K.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.46,0:18:22.98,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,- 嘿 - 嗨\N{\fs21}- Hey. - Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.98,0:18:24.70,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,让我给你补充下我今天晚上都做了什么\N{\fs21}Let me fill you in on the rest of my evening,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.70,0:18:26.75,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,这样你就不会觉得我有事瞒着你\N{\fs21}so you don't think I'm keeping anything from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.75,0:18:27.26,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,Will\N{\fs21}Will.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.26,0:18:29.31,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,回家路上 我从小贩那买了一份椒盐卷饼\N{\fs21}On the way home, I bought a pretzel from a vendor.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.31,0:18:32.87,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,我觉得他的名字是 Luba 我刮掉了上面一半的盐\N{\fs21}I think his name was Luba. And I scraped off half the salt.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.87,0:18:34.88,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,- 别这样 - 然后我去了书店\N{\fs21}- Come on. - Then I was in the bookstore
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.88,0:18:36.77,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,心不在焉地翻了翻\N{\fs21}and I was absentmindedly thumbing through
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.77,0:18:39.27,Note,,0,0,0,,美国女星 以超常记忆力闻名 七十年代出演剧集 Taxi
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.77,0:18:39.27,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,在垃圾桶里捡到的《Marilu Henner 的人生指南》\N{\fs21}"Marilu Henner's Guide To Life." It was in the bargain bin.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.27,0:18:42.45,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,你知道她从五岁开始就能劈叉了吗?\N{\fs21}She has been able to do the split since she was five?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.45,0:18:44.75,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,- 还有拇囊炎真是她的煎熬 - 我懂你的意思了\N{\fs21}- And bunions are her personal hell. - I get the point.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.75,0:18:46.48,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,然后 我快到家的时候\N{\fs21}Then, when I was almost home,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.48,0:18:48.15,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,我觉得我认出了街上的一个人\N{\fs21}I thought I recognized someone on the street,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.15,0:18:50.66,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,所以我抬手抬到一半想打招呼 却发现他不是我认识的那个人\N{\fs21}so I sort of half-waved, but then it wasn't who I thought it was,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.66,0:18:52.93,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,然后我就顺势假装挠了下耳朵… 只想让你知道\N{\fs21}so I pretended to scratch my ear-- just so you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.93,0:18:56.06,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,- 够了 见好就收! - 有什么大不了的 Grace?\N{\fs21}- Enough, already! - What's the deal, Grace?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.00,0:18:59.65,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,我没告诉你 Steven 的事又怎样 那只是场愚蠢的恋情\N{\fs21}So I don't tell you about Steven. It was a stupid affair.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.65,0:19:02.21,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,我并不为此感到自豪 我知道如果我告诉了你\N{\fs21}I wasn't particularly proud of it, and I knew if I told you,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.21,0:19:03.69,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,我就得真心地审视它\N{\fs21}I'd have to really examine it,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.69,0:19:05.89,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,但我只是真心想忘掉它\N{\fs21}when I really wanted it to go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.89,0:19:07.78,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,但 Will 如果我觉得你在隐瞒什么的话\N{\fs21}But, Will, if I think you're hiding something,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.78,0:19:09.24,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,我总是觉得你隐瞒的事情\N{\fs21}I'm always gonna think that you're hiding something
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.24,0:19:11.14,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,比实际情况要严重得多\N{\fs21}that's much bigger than it really is.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.14,0:19:13.08,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,你为什么会这样想?\N{\fs21}Why would you think that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.38,0:19:17.01,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,因为我不想再经历一遍你对我出柜的场景了\N{\fs21}Because I don't want you to tell me that you're gay again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.17,0:19:18.95,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,什么?\N{\fs21}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.58,0:19:22.37,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,我们读大学的时候 那时圣诞节休假中\N{\fs21}When we were in college, and at Christmas break
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.37,0:19:23.80,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,你对我出柜\N{\fs21}you told me you were gay,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.80,0:19:27.13,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,一切都不一样了\N{\fs21}everything changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.36,0:19:31.15,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,当然都不一样了 我整个人生都不一样了\N{\fs21}Of course it changed. My whole life changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.61,0:19:32.65,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,我的也是\N{\fs21}So did mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.11,0:19:38.26,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,所有事都解决了 但我总觉得我在隐隐等着\N{\fs21}Everything worked out, but I guess I'm just still waiting
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.26,0:19:40.11,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,你的下一个…\N{\fs21}for you to--
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.11,0:19:42.69,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,惊天大秘密来改变我的人生\N{\fs21}change my world with your next big secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.73,0:19:45.72,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,你差点就说了"颠覆我的世界" 对不对?\N{\fs21}You almost said "Rock my world," Didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.40,0:19:47.17,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,也许吧\N{\fs21}Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.84,0:19:48.89,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,Gracie...\N{\fs21}Gracie...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.23,0:19:54.32,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,出柜这种事 一生只用做一次的\N{\fs21}coming out of the closet is something you only do once in life.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.32,0:19:55.72,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,你要知道 就像出生一样\N{\fs21}You know, it's like being born
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.72,0:19:58.65,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,或者是看"魔术师"约翰逊的脱口秀\N{\fs21}or watching Magic Johnson's talk show.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.72,0:19:58.65,Note,,0,0,0,,美国著名篮球运动员 退役后开了一档脱口秀节目 The Magic Hour
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.28,0:20:04.57,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,我保证 不会再有惊心动魄的事情了\N{\fs21}I promise, no more big surprises.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.57,0:20:06.00,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,很好\N{\fs21}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.00,0:20:09.56,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,还有一件事我需要向你坦白\N{\fs21}There is one more I should tell you about.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.93,0:20:12.31,Main Sub,,0,0,0,,我怀孕了\N{\fs21}I'm pregnant.

